OL,3,CMan with cancer urges others to get
OL,4,Cearly diagnosis and have 'hope'
OL,6,FA man living with brain cancer has
OL,7,Fsaid "holding onto hope" and
OL,8,F"picturing a future" has helped keep
OL,9,Fhim going despite being told he could
OL,10,Fhave less than a year-and-a-half to
OL,11,Flive.
OL,13,FMatthew Collins, 37 from Aberdare, is
OL,14,Furging others to seek early diagnosis
OL,15,Fafter his brain tumour was detected "a
OL,16,Fgood few months" after he first
OL,17,Fnoticed symptoms.
