OL,3,CMan with cancer urges others to get
OL,4,Cearly diagnosis and have 'hope'
OL,6,FIt comes as new research shows more
OL,7,Fthan half of people diagnosed with
OL,8,Flung, liver, brain, oesophagus,
OL,9,Fpancreas or stomach cancers will die
OL,10,Fwithin one year.
OL,12,FThe Less Survivable Cancer Taskforce
OL,13,Fsaid there is a "five-year survival
OL,14,Frate of less than 20%" for people
OL,15,Fdiagnosed with these six cancers. It
OL,16,Fis calling for "better treatment and
OL,17,Fearlier diagnosis" to reduce the
OL,18,F"deadly cancer gap".
