OL,3,CMan with cancer urges others to get
OL,4,Cearly diagnosis and have 'hope'
OL,6,FMatthew Collins' symptoms started with
OL,7,Fsevere headaches. The 37-year-old said
OL,8,Fhe also suffered from seizures and
OL,9,Ftemporary blindness before having a
OL,10,Fstroke.
OL,12,FHe went to seek help but it took
OL,13,Fmonths of symptoms, repeated hospital
OL,14,Fvisits and scans, before the brain
OL,15,Ftumour was detected, which Matthew
OL,16,Fsaid was really "frustrating".
OL,18,F"I felt like I was just a burden to
OL,19,Fthem," he explained.
