OL,3,CMan with cancer urges others to get
OL,4,Cearly diagnosis and have 'hope'
OL,6,F"I didn't necessarily meet the
OL,7,Fcriteria for someone who would have a
OL,8,Fbrain tumour because I was so young
OL,9,Fand active.
OL,11,F"Then after diagnosis, it was
OL,12,Fdevastating to be told there were very
OL,13,Ffew treatment options."
OL,15,FSpeaking to ITV News, Matthew said the
OL,16,Fprognosis he was given was 12-18
OL,17,Fmonths. "I'm around the 15-month mark
OL,18,Fnow," he explained.
OL,20,F"I put that down to having hope and
OL,21,Fhaving something to live for."
