OL,3,CMan with cancer urges others to get
OL,4,Cearly diagnosis and have 'hope'
OL,6,FHe wants more to be done to ensure his
OL,7,Fkind of cancer is caught early.
OL,8,FMatthew said these cancers "represent
OL,9,Fthe biggest killer of under-40s but
OL,10,Fless than 1% of the research funding
OL,11,Fis spent on it".
OL,13,FThe Less Survivable Cancer Taskforce
OL,14,Fhas blamed "decades of underfunding"
OL,15,Ffor the prognosis inequalities.
OL,17,FResearch it has produced shows, "the
OL,18,Fchance of someone surviving for five
OL,19,Fyears after being diagnosed with one
OL,20,Fof these cancers is only 16%".
