OL,3,CMan with cancer urges others to get
OL,4,Cearly diagnosis and have 'hope'
OL,6,FJudi Rhys, the CEO of Tenovous Cancer
OL,7,FCare and the task force chair said the
OL,8,Ffigures are "really shocking".
OL,10,F"If you are diagnosed with one of
OL,11,Fthose less survivable cancers today,
OL,12,Fyour chance of survival are only 39% -
OL,13,Fthat's pretty awful. If you compare
OL,14,Fthat to all cancers, we have a 70%
OL,15,Fsurvival rate over a year so you can
OL,16,Fsee there is a lot of difference
OL,17,Fthere", she said.
