OL,3,CMan with cancer urges others to get
OL,4,Cearly diagnosis and have 'hope'
OL,6,FAccording to figures from the task
OL,7,Fforce, "more than 90,000 people are
OL,8,Fdiagnosed with one of the less
OL,9,Fsurvivable cancers in the UK every
OL,10,Fyear and they account for nearly half
OL,11,Fof all common cancer deaths".
OL,13,FIn a statement, a Welsh Government
OL,14,Fspokesperson said: "Our investment in
OL,15,Fcutting-edge cancer research in Wales
OL,16,Fcontinues to support Welsh researchers
OL,17,Fto contribute to the UK and global
OL,18,Fefforts to better diagnose and treat
OL,19,Fdifferent forms of cancer.
